headline: Marsh McLennan to Host Third Quarter Earnings Investor Call on October 16
summary: NEW YORK, September 18, 2025--Marsh McLennan (NYSE: MMC), a global leader in risk, strategy and people, will announce third quarter financial results via news release on Thursday, October 16, 2025, before the market opens. The news release will be available on marshmclennan.com.
